
🟢 AUTHENTICATION
TC_001
Module: Authentication
Description: Verify login with valid credentials
Preconditions: User account exists
Steps: Open site → Click login → Enter valid email & password → Submit
Expected Result: User should login successfully

TC_002
Description: Verify error for invalid password
Steps: Enter valid email + wrong password
Expected Result: Error message displayed

TC_003
Description: Verify login with empty fields
Steps: Leave fields empty → Click login
Expected Result: Validation message shown

TC_004
Description: Verify password is masked
Steps: Enter password in field
Expected Result: Password should not be visible

TC_005
Description: Verify login with invalid email format
Steps: Enter invalid email (abc@)
Expected Result: Validation error displayed

🔵 SEARCH

TC_006
Description: Verify search with valid product
Steps: Enter product name → Search
Expected Result: Relevant products displayed

TC_007
Description: Verify search with invalid keyword
Steps: Enter random text
Expected Result: No results / message displayed

TC_008
Description: Verify search with special characters
Steps: Enter @#$%
Expected Result: System handles input properly

TC_009
Description: Verify auto-suggestions
Steps: Start typing product
Expected Result: Suggestions appear

TC_010
Description: Verify search with long input string
Steps: Enter long text
Expected Result: System handles without crash

🟣 PRODUCT PAGE

TC_011
Description: Verify product details displayed
Steps: Open product page
Expected Result: Name, price, description visible

TC_012
Description: Verify product images load
Steps: Open product page
Expected Result: Images display properly

TC_013
Description: Verify product availability
Steps: Check product stock
Expected Result: Availability shown correctly

🟠 CART

TC_014
Description: Verify add to cart
Steps: Click “Add to Cart”
Expected Result: Product added to cart

TC_015
Description: Verify remove from cart
Steps: Remove item
Expected Result: Item removed successfully

TC_016
Description: Verify quantity update
Steps: Increase/decrease quantity
Expected Result: Cart updates correctly

TC_017
Description: Verify cart after refresh
Steps: Add item → Refresh page
Expected Result: Cart retains items

TC_018
Description: Verify multiple clicks on add to cart
Steps: Click add button multiple times
Expected Result: Proper quantity handling

🔴 CHECKOUT

TC_019
Description: Verify checkout process
Steps: Go to checkout
Expected Result: Checkout page loads

TC_020
Description: Verify checkout without login
Steps: Try checkout as guest
Expected Result: Prompt to login/signup

TC_021
Description: Verify empty cart checkout
Steps: Go to checkout with no items
Expected Result: Proper message displayed

TC_022
Description: Verify order summary
Steps: View summary page
Expected Result: Correct details shown

⚫ ADVANCED 

TC_023
Description: Verify session timeout
Steps: Stay inactive → Try action
Expected Result: Session expired message

TC_024
Description: Verify behavior on slow internet
Steps: Simulate slow network
Expected Result: System handles gracefully

TC_025
Description: Verify cart consistency across devices
Steps: Login on 2 devices → Modify cart
Expected Result: Cart syncs correctly